\ cancel mode verify
! graticule.jnl  (12/93)

! Description: Set the plot axis style to use a graticule (see GO tics)
! Note: the /GRATICULE qualifier on plot commands supersedes this script
!	with more-flexible control of graticule lines

! Usage:  GO graticule
! 	(to restore the normal tic style use  "GO tics")

! This script needs to be exectuted AFTER changes in aspect ratio
! (It uses the current axis lengths to set up)

ppl tics,,'ppl$ylen',,'ppl$xlen',1,1

set mode/last verify
